Keyindings for MPyC

Global Keys
'q'		-	exit MPyC
'1'		-	show current playlist
'2'		-	show Library
'3'		-	show this screen
'u'		-	update MPD Database

Playbackcontrol
'p'		-	toggle playing/paused
'+'		-	volume up
'-'		-	volume down
'>'		-	next song in playlist
'<'		-	previous song in playlist
'r'		-	set mode to random
'c'		-	set mode to consume
's'		-	set mode to single song
'w'		-	set more to repeat playlist

Movement Keys
'⬆' or 'k'	-	move up
'⬇' or 'j'	-	move down
'➡' or 'l'	-	enter directory (in library)
'⬅' or 'h'	-	one directory up (in library)


Playlist Keys
'⬆' or 'k'	-	move up
'⬇' or 'j'	-	move down
'd'		-	delete highlighted item from list
'SPACE'		-	play highlighted song
'ENTER'		-	play highlighted song
'K'		-	swap with song one above
'J'		-	swap with song one below


Library Keys
'⬆' or 'k'	-	move up
'⬇' or 'j'	-	move down
'➡' or 'l'	-	enter directory
'⬅' or 'h'	-	one directory up
'SPACE'		-	add directory or file to playlist
'ENTER'		-	add directory of file to playlist
